Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.08,0:00:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九 看来我也许确实错了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道定量的蛋糕买不光会怎样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那可真是让人伤心透了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.97,0:00:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别 甜品 专柜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我改成了下单才做的制度了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使在这种乡下 需求也还是有的呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在卖得不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.11,0:00:29.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.82,0:00:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柜台 电话还是互联网们都可以订购
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.49,0:00:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互网网…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互联网…网…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互联…互联…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,互联网啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.93,0:01:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是互聊网啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 你刚刚把什么藏起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我在写目记
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.98,0:01:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉 比起这个你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.11,0:01:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也搞互联网网购!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你要买漫画吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系介样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:54.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗点心和店里的玩具之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过网络来卖对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:03:00.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实现在那样做会比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以为此我们要先做出我们店的主页
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:07.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先尝试着…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.35,0:03:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了一个看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一是互联网强人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hypertext Markup Language什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是义务教育级别的水平啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个有名的HTML…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么这个样子的话太朴素了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么东西跟着跟随着鼠标的移动在闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个超级怀念的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.67,0:03:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Java Script哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.25,0:03:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是那个有名的Java Script
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.30,0:03:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 电脑什么都能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是文明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:50.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先卖些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…比如说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传要点是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传…宣传要点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:02.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我们卖粗点心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.21,0:04:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宣传过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字咻地飘过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么老长的文字咻地不停飘过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个再这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.68,0:04:32.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很…很闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把在卖粗点心的乱强调一气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是粗点心店嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿田粗点心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么感觉变得这么有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.53,0:04:46.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这张照片上传 放到主页上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是店长（暂定）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛有打上码的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再把这个这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多个我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 难得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:19.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也把我放上去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.15,0:05:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打码太麻烦了 用手代替
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后 写上粗点心能送货上门还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后还要写什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.32,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有粗点心店的怀旧之情之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个部分强调一下的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以 怀旧感对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.91,0:05:38.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:44.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「鹿田」员工 一酱（ 20岁 ）给你最淳朴的味道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.96,0:05:46.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.43,0:05:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是在做粗点心店的宣传而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 我们也卖玩员之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:06:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,☆也有玩具…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是… 配送粗点心这也输进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得有点太过火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全就是乘兴做过头的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我重做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.00,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是于是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 订货估计会在中午前送到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店长你订了什么货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你说交给你来订的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说你忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这怎么可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:46.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑 开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然今天就会送到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘记啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 现在网购的话今天还送得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个吧 超级弹力球
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 反正也不是什座热卖商品…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.63,0:07:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…于是就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.22,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:11.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢…欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪 一个超级弹力球都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的啊 这店真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 现在断货了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还特意起了个早想中个大的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得粗点心店重新开业 这不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:34.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么看来马上又要关门了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去便利店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了 这么下去这几个小孩儿就不会再来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好想想 好好思考下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.38,0:07:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等 少年们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.17,0:07:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们难道不想要大号的弹力球…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.88,0:07:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要"自已想要的"尺寸的弹力球吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐和水还有洗衣液 以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.52,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是指这个 弹力球呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.94,0:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是猴急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样可变不成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 在杯装的冰里加入食盐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后搅拌均匀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着加入洗衣浆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 那边猴急的你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢什么颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:28.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我才不猴急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是急性子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.42,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这里就选姐姐喜欧的孔雀蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在杯子里加一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杷这个好好搅拌的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:47.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹力球就出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.98,0:08:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不是球形的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是性急啊 这样会不受女孩子欢迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:09:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个滴溜滴溜地搓圆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水分挤出来了就擦干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就擦在衣服上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.58,0:09:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搓搓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 这就是你专用的弹力球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.71,0:09:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…专用 专用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 姐姐你是炼金术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要 也帮我做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:23.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好 一个30日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:30.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.78,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是先混过去了
